{"tid":1248810,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"21號行動檢討","createTime":"2019-06-21T14:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T14:38:15.000Z","uid":195186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0967a21e3a7cf7cc3b93316e364fc11d792e3aa","tid":1248810,"uid":195186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"發夢夢到大家今日好齊心<br />\n一有人衝都係叫唔好衝<br />\n不過有幾點想大家留意下<br />\n-<br />\n1.現場係有狗拍緊片<br />\n2.好似傳物資咁 聽到人嗌乜<br />\n覺得有價值既嗌出去俾其他人知<br />\n3.有人做緊adc果陣係有記者影緊<br />\n-<br />\n以下係細佬既小小意見:<br />\n1.當有狗拍片果陣 保護自己 保護身邊既人<br />\n開著你既電筒 好似演唱會咁<br />\n<br />\n2.同1差不多 聽到有人嗌開電筒麻煩同身邊師兄講下<br />\n又或者嗌出去 都係果句:保護自己 保護身邊既人<br />\n<br />\n3.我唔知我多心定點 我見到現場係有記者鬼鬼祟祟<br />\n見到呢d麻煩提一提身邊既師兄 唔好有機會俾人入到<br />\n<br />\n有既可以補充下<br />\n第1次開呢d正經po 請輕插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c650caa3cf1d2bd15f19a51057e50668ee12286","tid":1248810,"uid":195186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"小推1下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1eafff457e5f1b309098a30c1fd9f1efb2c515","tid":1248810,"uid":195186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"小推2下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287d596644bd921139cb4d354783e6353d9b16fb","tid":1248810,"uid":195186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"小推3下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c621991587b80ce12f9a761cc19a8f2566b66209","tid":1248810,"uid":195186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"小推4下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8000875e576ff09b20b665f4ae6ec4109c4cd4ea","tid":1248810,"uid":195186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:38:15